Railstats LA

Project Overview

Status:

Completed

Partner: LA Metro

Location: Remote

Links: GitHub, Site

Tools: Docker, AWS, Observable

Languages:

Railstats LA tracks LA Metro trains and generates punctuality reports. Our website enables both Metro officials and the public to easily review up-to-date statistics for LA's 6 train lines.

If you would like to talk to us about this completed project, please reach out to team@hackforla.org
